# NOTE: models/weights/ is intentionally NOT excluded. The recognition code
# (app/api/recognition.py) resolves models relative to the repo root, so the
# weights must be present inside the image for CRNN / TrOCR to load. If we
# later decide to download weights lazily at runtime (same pattern as PaddleX),
# we can exclude models/weights/ and drop ~1.4 GB from the image.
